a:17:{s:4:"name";s:14:"Rumalaya forte";s:11:"small_descr";s:88:"Rumalaya forte is an effective anti-inflammatory analgesic with immunomodulatory action.";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:101:"Rumalaya Forte ist ein effektives entzündungshemmendes Analgetikum mit immunmodulatorischer Wirkung.";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:95:"Rumalaya Forte est un analgésique anti-inflammatoire efficace avec l'action immunomodulatrice.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:87:"Rumalaya Forte es un analgésico anti-inflamatorio eficaz con acción inmunomoduladora.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:87:"Rumalaya forte è un analgesico anti-infiammatorio efficace con azione immunomodulante.";s:10:"full_descr";s:1340:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Rumalaya forte is an effective anti-inflammatory analgesic with immunomodulatory action.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCTIONS&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Take it as prescribed by your doctor.</p><p><strong>DOSAGE</strong></p><p>Please consult your physician to prescribe the dosage that best suits your condition.</p><p><strong>STORAGE&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Store at the room temperature away from moisture and sunlight. Keep out of reach of children.</p><p>MORE INFO:<br /><br />The medicine is composed of:</p><p>Shallaki (Boswellia serrata)<br />Guggulu Suddha (Commiphora wightii)	&nbsp;<br />Rasna (Alpinia galanga)	&nbsp;<br /> Yashti-madhu (Glycyrrhiza glabra)</p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p>Rumalaya forte is not known to have any warnings and precautions.</p><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>Rumalaya forte tablet is not known to have any side effects if taken as per the prescribed dosage.</p><p><strong>More Information</strong><br /><br />Rumalaya forte tablet is useful for the treatment of:</p><p>- Rheumatoid arthritis</p><p>- Osteoarthritis</p><p>- Cervical and lumbar spondylosis</p><p>- Traumatic inflammatory conditions like fibrositis, bursitis, synovitis, capsulitis, tenosynovitis, myositis and sciatica</p><p>- Arthralgia</p><p>- Gout</p><p>- Frozen should